      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine, flawless shape. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
