    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccably maintained 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2), a pinnacle of analog driver engagement. This wide-body example features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical provenance is verified, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a clean bore-scope inspection. The factory Turbo-spec suspension and four-piston monoblock calipers provide exceptional lateral grip and deceleration. Finished in its original paint with zero track-use wear, the chassis remains stiff and responsive, while the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. This is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
