    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, while the carpets and trim pieces appear untouched. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, boasting a comprehensive service history and a drive feel that is tight, responsive, and completely silent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
